import { 
  Container, 
  Typography, 
  Grid, 
  Card, 
  CardContent, 
  CardMedia,
  Box,
  Divider,
  Stack,
  Chip,
  useTheme
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';

const StyledSection = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({
  marginBottom: theme.spacing(6),
}));

const teamMembers = [
  {
    name: 'John Doe',
    role: 'Frontend Developer',
    contributions: 'UI design, React components, dashboard',
    image: '/team/john-doe.jpg' // Add actual image paths
  },
  {
    name: 'Jane Smith',
    role: 'Backend Developer',
    contributions: 'APIs, file upload, JWT auth',
    image: '/team/jane-smith.jpg'
  },
  {
    name: 'Alex Roy',
    role: 'AI Engineer',
    contributions: 'Chart recommendation engine',
    image: '/team/alex-roy.jpg'
  },
  {
    name: 'Priya Patel',
    role: 'Full-stack',
    contributions: 'MongoDB schema, integration, bug fixing',
    image: '/team/priya-patel.jpg'
  }
];

const techStack = [
  'React.js',
  'Material UI',
  'Node.js',
  'Express',
  'MongoDB',
  'Mongoose',
  'Chart.js'
];

export default function AboutUs() {
  const theme = useTheme();
  
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 4 }}>
      {/* Mission Section */}
      <StyledSection>
        <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom>
          About DataViz Pro
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
          Transforming data visualization through AI-powered insights
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          DataViz Pro revolutionizes how you interact with data by automatically recommending
          the most effective visualizations for your datasets. Our platform combines
          cutting-edge AI with intuitive design to make data visualization accessible to everyone.
        </Typography>
      </StyledSection>

      {/* Features Section */}
      <StyledSection>
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          Key Features
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card elevation={2} sx={{ height: '100%', transition: 'transform 0.3s', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-5px)' } }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>Smart Upload</Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Seamless CSV/JSON file upload with automatic data parsing
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card elevation={2} sx={{ height: '100%', transition: 'transform 0.3s', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-5px)' } }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>AI Recommendations</Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Intelligent chart suggestions based on your data structure
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card elevation={2} sx={{ height: '100%', transition: 'transform 0.3s', '&:hover': { transform: 'translateY(-5px)' } }}>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>Interactive Charts</Typography>
                <Typography>
                  Dynamic, responsive visualizations powered by Chart.js
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </StyledSection>

      {/* Tech Stack Section */}
      <StyledSection>
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          Tech Stack
        </Typography>
        <Stack direction="row" spacing={1} flexWrap="wrap" gap={1} sx={{ marginTop: 2 }}>
          {techStack.map((tech) => (
            <Chip 
              key={tech} 
              label={tech} 
              color="primary" 
              sx={{ 
                fontSize: '0.875rem',
                fontWeight: 500
              }} 
            />
          ))}
        </Stack>
      </StyledSection>

      {/* Team Section */}
      <StyledSection>
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          Meet Our Team
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {teamMembers.map((member) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={member.name}>
              <Card 
                elevation={3} 
                sx={{ 
                  height: '100%',
                  transition: 'transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s',
                  '&:hover': { 
                    transform: 'translateY(-8px)',
                    boxShadow: theme.shadows[6]
                  } 
                }}
              >
                <CardMedia
                  component="img"
                  height="200"
                  image={member.image}
                  alt={member.name}
                  sx={{ objectFit: 'cover' }}
                />
                <CardContent>
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>{member.name}</Typography>
                  <Typography color="primary" fontWeight="medium" gutterBottom>{member.role}</Typography>
                  <Divider sx={{ my: 1 }} />
                  <Typography variant="body2">{member.contributions}</Typography>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </StyledSection>

      {/* Future Scope Section */}
      <StyledSection>
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          Future Scope
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          We're constantly working to enhance DataViz Pro. Our roadmap includes:
        </Typography>
        <Box sx={{ pl: 3 }}>
          <Typography component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Excel and spreadsheet support</Typography>
          <Typography component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Real-time collaboration features</Typography>
          <Typography component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Cloud storage integration</Typography>
          <Typography component="li" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>Advanced AI-powered analytics</Typography>
        </Box>
      </StyledSection>
    </Container>
  );
}
